BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-12T13:29:59&endDate=2026-07-13T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMinor delays between Paddington and Heathrow Terminals / Reading while we fix a track fault between Acton Main Line and Paddington. Tickets are being accepted by Great Western Railway. All day on Sunday\, 12 July\, service will operate at a reduced frequency between Whitechapel and Shenfield while we undertake repairs following a line side fire at Stratford on Friday. GOOD SERVICE on the rest of the line. 
